## ğŸ§  Summary of Findings

| Area | Key Takeaways |
|------|----------------|
| **Sales Trend** | Strong Q4 performance, peak in November (Â£1.17M). |
| **Countries** | UK leads; strong secondary markets in EIRE & Netherlands. |
| **Products** | A few SKUs generate a large proportion of total sales. |
| **Customers** | High loyalty; opportunity for reactivation of "At Risk" customers. |
| **Seasonality** | Clear holiday-driven purchasing pattern. |

