## âš™ï¸ How to Recreate in Tableau

1. Open Tableau â†’ **Connect â†’ Text file â†’ `online_retail_cleaned.csv`**  
2. Add another data source â†’ `online_retail_rfm.csv`  
3. (Optional) Blend on **Customer ID**  
4. Recreate visuals as above  
5. Combine into a unified dashboard using the layout plan  

